credit.credit-words: Jesus lives! henceforth is death But the gate of life immortal; This shall calm our trembling breath, When we pass its gloomy portal. Alleluia!
Jesus lives! for us He died; Then, alone to Jesus living Pure in heart may abide, Glory to our Savior giving. Alleluia!
Jesus lives! to Him the throne Over all the world is given; May we go where He is gone, Rest and reign with Him in heaven. Alleluia!
